%N A003077 Decimal expansion of 22/7 - Pi.
%C A003077 The integral representation of this constant, with a positive integrand, was apparently first published by the British electrical engineer Donald Percy Dalzell (1898-1988) in 1944. - _Amiram Eldar_, Jul 02 2026
